secp256k1
-----------------------
The implementation of the native ECDSA speedup package "btc/newec" is based on the code created 
by Pieter Wuille. The code itself has been completely rewritten, but the original author deserves
a credit for all the algorithms.
 * https://github.com/sipa/secp256k1/blob/master/COPYING


bitcoin-qt
-----------------------
Some parts of the source code (e.g. "btc/target.go") and some test vectors ("btc/test/*.json")
were taken from the original (satoshi's) bitcoin client.
 * https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/COPYING

